{"tid":675729,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【法庭影相】庭內拍照內地女身份曝光 任職央企中鐵建","createTime":"2018-05-23T18:56:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T01:46:16.000Z","uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6c06418aefe98b38390cdec52fa2915722a41f42","tid":675729,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T18:56:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180523/large/1527087671_024e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180523%2Flarge%2F1527087671_024e.png&h=85f6b789&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180523/large/1527087828_7194.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180523%2Flarge%2F1527087828_7194.png&h=c17c71f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佔旺藐視法庭案件今於高院續審，其間有內地女子在庭內拍照，被法官充公手機，亦不准她離開香港。<br />\n<br />\n本報翻查紀錄，該名女子名為唐琳，英文名為Aileen Tang，現時為央企中國鐵建（1186）投資部副總經理，卡片稱自己屬註冊會計師（CPA）及律師（Barrister-at-Law），其聯絡地址雖然為北京，但印有香港及內地手機號碼，證明其常來香港，有人亦曾經在長和（001）及長實（1113）股東會時，目睹其在九龍海逸君綽酒店出沒，但當時她既非股東，亦非股東代表身份。<br />\n其Linkedin資料顯示，她2012年於悉尼大學碩士畢業，主修會計及金融，其後加入中金（3908）任投資經理，及後任職中交建（1800）收購及合併經理，再轉至目前中鐵建職位，三間公司都有濃厚中國央企背景。<br />\n<br />\n而其微信朋友圈張貼多張在法庭內的拍照，包括在第二十八法庭外拍照，以及一張籌號，其微信上<span style=\"color: red;\">寫上「No.1 Tocket」，疑似串錯「Ticket」</span>，並配了哈哈笑圖案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180523/58229680\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180523%2F58229680&d=GvMfIaxsAroam1iGpigVBpzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=5c11d26e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180523%2F58229680&h=68f96494\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180523/58229680</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180524/large/1527093218_3c13.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180524%2Flarge%2F1527093218_3c13.jpg&h=fd1f812f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 副總經理"},{"pid":"8eb816ec3aa548b9aa39f062ae9e5580bc79b4f2","tid":675729,"uid":36901,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T19:07:08.000Z","msg":"d英文垃撚圾到speak up stand up都唔識分,屎撚過香港d小學雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c68798dc5f24abbf8b7e9fa78bb77d784a5e1ecf","tid":675729,"uid":17646,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T19:29:03.000Z","msg":"CPA唔識英文，請槍？"},{"pid":"0016da8c0e23fe33da2bde54531a98d1a9b93eeb","tid":675729,"uid":99205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T20:04:03.000Z","msg":"支那人乜撚都求求其其<br />\n做個樣咪得"},{"pid":"78179e04c20a4863645418777f937efc25e18bdf","tid":675729,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T20:08:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/24/040829_4c2924a566426afa8523e1593c75a358.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F24%2F040829_4c2924a566426afa8523e1593c75a358.gif&h=d2f68c67&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f6effa7bd3dfe87a12ab121827b5041cdae6bd74","tid":675729,"uid":143288,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T20:55:39.000Z","msg":"悉尼大學碩士畢業<br />\nTocket我當佢打錯<br />\nSpeak up stand up 點有可能錯啊張沙紙係咪淘寶返嚟架"},{"pid":"61c47b10032617e8741082569407fd31ae15baaa","tid":675729,"uid":96486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T21:09:40.000Z","msg":"望著香港法律比個大陸人任意踐踏真係好正"},{"pid":"190d3086e8535af69598c129cc28c635fd79ea33","tid":675729,"uid":5267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T01:43:47.000Z","msg":"此回